625
00:28:07,480 --> 00:28:09,160
not what he did in the past.

626
00:28:12,270 --> 00:28:13,400
(The past.)

627
00:28:14,350 --> 00:28:15,680
(What if Chen Shan)

628
00:28:15,680 --> 00:28:17,720
