629
00:28:23,880 --> 00:28:25,400
Look at you.

630
00:28:25,400 --> 00:28:27,240
Are you thinking of someone?

631
00:28:27,240 --> 00:28:29,000
Just keep drinking.

632
00:28:33,200 --> 00:28:33,960
Do you need me

633
00:28:33,960 --> 00:28:34,920
